      - Console-log evidence that `detail` + unknown extensions are
        captured for diagnostics (Test 7 trace).
      - Correlation-id propagation verification — pick one error code,
        capture End-to-end trace ID through App Insights / Kusto if
        accessible (smoke test environment).
      - BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB (confirmed; no `dotnet publish`
        run for this task).
      - Zero new dependencies (verified via package.json diff).
      - `code-review` + `adr-check` pass results.

      Report task completion + handoff to task 030 (Insights tool smoke
      tests).
    </step>
  </steps>

