    <criterion testable="true">Renderer integrates with EXISTING `InsightsResponseRenderer` from task 026 — no parallel error-rendering component created (reuse mandate per R5 CLAUDE.md §3.1). Confirmed by grep + reviewer inspection.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">No new feature flags introduced (R5 CLAUDE.md §3.2 / ADR-018); retry policies are unconditional; backoff timing hard-coded per integration brief contract. Confirmed by `adr-check` pass at Step 9.5.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">**Zone B boundary verified**: renderer files import NOTHING from `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/...`; error envelope parsed via R5-local TypeScript types matching contract wire shape (per R5 CLAUDE.md §3.5 + refined ADR-013 §3.5). Confirmed by grep + reviewer inspection at Step 9.5.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">v1.1 forward-compat: ProblemDetails TypeScript type includes `[key: string]: unknown` index signature; unknown extensions Console-logged but not rendered. Confirmed by Test 7 (leakage canary asserts unknown extensions don't leak).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB (confirmed in task notes; no BFF code changed by this task). No new frontend dependencies introduced (confirmed by package.json diff in task notes).</criterion>
